# Exclude local build artifacts from the Docker build context.
#
# WHY THIS MATTERS for the build-test image:
#   The build-base image pre-installs scoop at C:/toolset-repo/build/scoop.
#   If you have run build.ps1 locally, a build/ folder exists in your workspace.
#   Without this file, "docker build" would send that folder as part of the build
#   context, and "COPY . ." in Dockerfile.build-test would overwrite the base
#   image's pre-installed scoop with your local copy.
#
# If you have never run build.ps1 locally, this file has no effect.
build/
*.log
